<!-- the abstract for the resource. If not provided, the XSL will use the in scope -->
 <abstract>
    <p>This document specifies the use of ISO 10303 integrated resources satisfying the
	requirements for providing text and symbology applied to either a drawing sheet, drawing view, a
	piece of annotation, or a draughting shape model, for the purpose of communicating product data
	and drawing interpretation information.</p>
 </abstract>

