   <projlead ref="markus.maier"/>
   <editor ref="markus.maier"/>
 </contacts>

 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
    This document specifies the application interpreted construct for the description of annotation presented
	on a drawing that has a specific meaning or purpose within the scope of draughting. 
	Annotation, in the form of text and symbology, provides additional product data that may be needed to fully define the
	product or interpret the drawing.
   </p>
 </purpose>

